wight fighter, won gold forAlgeriain the 66kg category, but her bouts wereovershadowed by the heated debate and she faced a barrage of online abuse.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 25-year-old welterwight fighter\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"the 66kg category\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"her bouts\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"the heated debate\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 529}, {\"ngram\": \"a barrage\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was disqualified from the World Championships last year when the International Boxing Association (IBA) announced she had failed a gender eligibility test.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.279583143116192e-24, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999983815542, \"rank\": 1.6185605489725914e-09, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"a gender eligibility test\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she was cleared to compete in Paris by the International Olympic Committee andwent on to win the gold.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.582121829931988e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The boxer has filed a criminal complaint with the Paris prosecutor's office, alleging aggravated cyber harassment and a \\\"misogynist, racist and sexist campaign\\\" against her.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.582121829931988e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The boxer\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"a criminal complaint\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"aggravated cyber harassment\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"misogynist, racist and sexist campaign\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 1003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's lawyer, Nabil Boudi, has now revealed that Harry Potter author Rowling and X/Twitter owner Musk have been named in the legal complaint, while former US President Donald Trump may also be in the firing line.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 0.9999999999267857, \"rank\": 7.292551644010797e-11, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}, {\"begin\": 1177, \"end\": 1189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999150272779, \"rank\": 8.495991897683465e-08, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif's lawyer\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"Nabil Boudi\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"the legal complaint\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"the firing line\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What we are asking is that the prosecution investigates not only these people but whoever it feels necessary\\\", he said.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prosecution\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"not only these people\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"whoever\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1326}]}, {