igital lynching\\\".\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3121, \"end\": 3127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8236541302612159, \"rank\": 0.2069348735310355, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her legal complaint\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"the online abuse\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"digital lynching\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA, which is locked in a separate dispute with the IOC over claims of corruption, has refused to share details of its gender tests, but had written to the Olympic authorities more than a year ago to say that Khelif has the DNA of a \\\"male\\\".\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3206, \"end\": 3209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999983815542, \"rank\": 1.6185605489725914e-09, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 3258, \"end\": 3261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.38992726105551e-26, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a separate dispute\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"claims\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"corruption\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3287}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"its gender tests\", \"from\"